## FAQ

**Q: Do I need coding skills to build an AI website chatbot?**
A: No. Modern Enterprise platforms allow you to build, train, configure, and deploy intelligent AI chatbots using an intuitive, visual no-code interface.

**Q: Can the chatbot understand multiple languages?**
A: Yes, advanced conversational AI platforms natively support over 50 languages. They can automatically detect the user's language and translate complex technical interactions in real time.

**Q: What happens if the chatbot doesn't know the answer to a question?**
A: A properly configured AI will politely inform the user and gracefully transfer the ongoing conversation to an available human agent, automatically providing the agent with the full chat history for seamless continuity.

**Q: How long does it typically take to implement a website chatbot?**
A: Unlike legacy systems that took months to build, with a modern no-code platform you can ingest your knowledge, test, and deploy a custom AI agent to your live website in just a few days or even hours.

**Q: Is my proprietary company data secure when training the AI?**
A: Yes, enterprise-grade AI platforms adhere to strict, industry-leading security and compliance standards, such as GDPR, ISO 27001, and SOC 2, ensuring your data is protected and never used to train public models.

